@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ocpfiv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.abs(v0 + 0.13) * 0.69))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin((v1 + 0.90 * v0 + 0.11)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos((v2 + 0.76 / tmp + 0.03)))
    tmp = wp.abs((v1 - v0))
    v0 = (wp.sin(tmp) - ((v0 + 0.88 * v2 + 0.16) * v1))
    v2 = 0.66
    data[tid] = v0
